text: Alice Sakitnak Akammak (born 1940) is an Innu artist. Her work is included in the collections of the Winnipeg Art Gallery, the Canadian Museum of History, Musée national des beaux-arts du Québec, and the McMichael Canadian Art Collection ==References== Category:1940 births Category:20th-century Canadian women artists Category:21st-century Canadian women artists Category:Living people Category:Inuit artists
